[stdout] {"type":"step_start","timestamp":1772606575192,"sessionID":"ses_3486a349dffeKm455bWDGdjJ0E","part":{"id":"prt_cb795d251001xcvd1E2XQ1NSU8","sessionID":"ses_3486a349dffeKm455bWDGdjJ0E","messageID":"msg_cb795ccda001tXsqtFa56F2X2d","type":"step-start"}}

[stdout] {"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1772606575377,"sessionID":"ses_3486a349dffeKm455bWDGdjJ0E","part":{"id":"prt_cb795d2cd001KZunpVolNY8PWS","sessionID":"ses_3486a349dffeKm455bWDGdjJ0E","messageID":"msg_cb795ccda001tXsqtFa56F2X2d","type":"tool","callID":"call_fOa5C3rhtrPnvofub1Z7h8ld","tool":"skill","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"name":"tscircuit"},"output":"<skill_content name=\"tscircuit\">\n# Skill: tscircuit\n\n# tscircuit\n\nYou are helping the user design electronics using tscircuit (React/TypeScript) and the `tsci` CLI.\n\nWhen this Skill is active:\n\n- Prefer tscircuit’s documented primitives and CLI behavior. If something is unclear, confirm by:\n  - Reading local files in the repo (e.g., `tscircuit.config.json`, `index.tsx`, `package.json`)\n  - Running `tsci --help` or the specific subcommand’s `--help`\n- Avoid “inventing” JSX props or CLI flags.\n\n## Default workflow\n\n1) Clarify requirements (if not already given)\n- Board form factor / size constraints\n- Power sources and voltage rails\n- I/O: connectors, headers, mounting holes, mechanical constraints\n- Target manufacturer constraints (trace/space, assembly, supplier)\n\n2) Choose a starting point\n- If the repo is not a tscircuit project, recommend:\n  - Install CLI, then `tsci init` to bootstrap a project.\n- If a form-factor template is appropriate (Arduino Shield, Raspberry Pi HAT, etc.), prefer `@tscircuit/common` templates.\n\n3) Find and install components\n- Use `tsci search \"<query>\"` to discover footprints and tscircuit registry packages.\n- Use one of:\n  - `tsci add <author/pkg>` for registry packages (installs `@tsci/*` packages)\n  - `tsci import <query>` when you need to import a component from JLCPCB or the registry.\n\n4) Write/modify TSX circuit code\n- Keep circuits as a default-exported function that returns JSX.\n- Use layout props intentionally:\n  - PCB: `pcbX`, `pcbY`, `pcbRotation`, `layer`\n  - Schematic: `schX`, `schY`, `schRotation`, `schOrientation`\n- Use `<trace />` for connectivity; prefer net connections (`net.GND`, `net.VCC`, etc.) for power/ground.\n\n5) Build and iterate\n- Run `tsci build` to compile and validate the circuit.\n- DRC (Design Rule Check) errors can often be ignored during development—focus on getting the circuit correct first.\n- If routing struggles, reduce density, use `<group />` for sub-layouts, or change autorouter settings.\n- Use `tsci dev` only when you need interactive visual feedback (not typical for AI-driven iteration).\n\n6) Validate and export\n- Run `tsci build` (and optionally `tsci snapshot`) before sharing/publishing.\n- Use `tsci export` for SVG/netlist/DSN/3D/library outputs.\n- For manufacturing, obtain fabrication outputs (Gerbers/BOM/PnP) from the export UI after `tsci dev`.\n\n## Safety and non-goals\n\n- Treat electrical safety, regulatory compliance, and manufacturability as user-owned responsibilities.\n- Do not publish (`tsci push`) or place orders unless the user explicitly requests it.\n\n## Local references bundled with this Skill\n\n- CLI primer: `CLI.md`\n- Syntax primer: `SYNTAX.md`\n- Workflow patterns: `WORKFLOW.md`\n- Pre-export checklist: `CHECKLIST.md`\n- Ready-to-copy templates: `templates/`\n- Helper scripts: `scripts/`\n\nBase directory for this skill: file:///workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit\nRelative paths in this skill (e.g., scripts/, reference/) are relative to this base directory.\nNote: file list is sampled.\n\n<skill_files>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/templates/group-layout.tsx</file>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/templates/arduino-shield-led.tsx</file>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/templates/minimal-board.tsx</file>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/templates/chip-with-pinouts.tsx</file>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/CHECKLIST.md</file>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/WORKFLOW.md</file>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/README.md</file>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/CLI.md</file>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/scripts/smoke_test.sh</file>\n<file>/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit/scripts/export_svgs.sh</file>\n</skill_files>\n</skill_content>","title":"Loaded skill: tscircuit","metadata":{"name":"tscircuit","dir":"/workspace/.claude/skills/tscircuit","truncated":false},"time":{"start":1772606575363,"end":1772606575375}},"metadata":{"openrouter":{"reasoning_details":[{"type":"reasoning.summary","summary":"**Prior","format":"openai-responses-v1","index":0},{"type":"reasoning.summary","summary":"it","format":"openai-responses-v1","index":0},{"type":"reasoning.summary","summary":"izing","format":"openai-responses-v1","index":0},{"type":"reasoning.summary","summary":" skill","format":"openai-responses-v1","index":0},{"type":"reasoning.summary","summary":" invocation","format":"openai-responses-v1","index":0},{"type":"reasoning.summary","summary":"**","format":"openai-responses-v1","index":0},{"type":"reasoning.encrypted","data":"gAAAAABpp9Rv2njO6QROLF32Wht7jLzPOs72PhoXbCOAxbpIAriUarxNK2gx7LoCrA90fZ33Xko8AlZVOhpNbcs9yHfOyJ3w4AXtjHhcO5wlMBujmujBxMwH4mZWRPpPV4TWvUHwE3aY8KbnvsriREGIW1XRgeofgtmTv3RYXaXaJ4_b-9v_CFiHY7SxWVsBOposI-e9CL0hl0s7gE097Y1IglN7vjLNaxz4r9yTOZuuJ-5eJpfGptTKlCoR5SV0-nBaLrT9N-chCUb__5CjiKX36x4Ph7GYJzLm0op7SnMaESruYsA8NUO06ByN1klyCfje0SqnobAVC-8842QT7EzBEgVNXYFBGCC6Q8QBLAjozSk4o9-b9vWIf5OudTzwzE9RjTUkNq-C-ojZ3U6mZQq9ExySULE_aW_M4VkcBssVI2sLlOagRw2bPBar5djNV7I8wOQAVzcbSC6lYh9asGNCFJGEpYgzq6rPFjmzeiW3vzTqpbLJCEkovVwLFrp8lICBX991y80EJ4p27SiyuK_mLKOz_J0gs8hnxf-Wjxp7ObSS5Y5oDjOlV7dcG-J8Rer3kqyNhk4M-m8Ty_gWiI2JGI3LBA7XCK7wbbC1eLu_u-V0RyZXifqHwi61d3vb5WXx7PwWugmrCoB6PCN0J5yTcIp2YxNyruaD00avyP9kAhtIIEMuDkwoiMlKhVIlFyI8VR_LhoSqs9zcU_RbJdMKEkKTb9eneYrq6oJYN4i6DZBgxoWbNqfHoA5H-0fF1L0-cffYGnbirOXxWPSPaZYzUvCmDsI6exbnsA8tBM1LW1XkRw4AmrZ0q29yPcJpYy3bMQvzjrKfImXDX4XPhqxq_8GEkOKSZSkyu7qVqkfgmBsDyxAeZTYvUjcl4wPU6kRGjSl0X5uKqCqWUFWJommkLivlGqjyuI4hVrouD01XV0P_SqKRRladaGq5ZTKAlmQ85r5092kw","id":"rs_067c